Euro 2016: Pick your Northern Ireland starting XI

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Northern Ireland will make history in France this summer when they compete at a European Championship finals for the first time.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Michael O'Neill's team finished top of qualifying Group F and will take on Poland, Germany and Ukraine at Euro 2016.
But who would you pick to face the Poles in NI's opening game on Sunday, 12 June?
